def escape(text):
    """
    Minimal HTML escaping, not for attribute values (unlike html.escape).
    """
    if not isinstance(text, str):
        text = str(text)
    # Replace & first to avoid double escaping
    text = text.replace("&", "&")
    text = text.replace("<", "<")
    text = text.replace(">", ">")
    text = text.replace('"', """)
    text = text.replace("'", "'")
    return text
